result.execSummary:
The defendant Thomas E Daleb was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Thomas E Daleb is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Thomas E Daleb was found guilty of Possession of Cocaine/Coca, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(c).
  • Thomas E Daleb was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
